{"tid":2442023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬鋼琴女神 Live彈琴失準後收負評 現場直接失控","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T07:02:48.000Z","uid":345353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33f2bd33c4bdd4723f6420be2f44e55c0e2f7d5f","tid":2442023,"uid":345353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞有影響力人物李元玲（Cathryn Li）在網上出名而聞名。 在網友對她的鋼琴技巧發表了冷酷的評論之後，看到她發脾氣，真是令人驚訝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFXuENH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFXuENH.png&h=aef6c731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正面交鋒FaceTalk主持人Andy Chan今天在Facebook Live的脫口秀節目中邀請了Cathryn Li作為特邀嘉賓。 除了因Insta出名外，Cathryn還是一位女演員，偶爾還會彈鋼琴。 她甚至在YouTube頻道上上傳了鋼琴演奏的視頻。 在脫口秀節目中的某一時刻，Andy 要求她與他的Jam歌，以展示自己的鋼琴演奏技巧。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6FHfk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6FHfk2.png&h=8e2d09f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當主持人自己彈歌時，她看上去很無聊和尷尬。 他們演奏後，李元玲：&ldquo;有人罵我&quot;，然後聲稱&rdquo;所有評論都在&ldquo;嘲笑&rdquo;我&quot;。 <br />\n<br />\n發脾氣 Video:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QIRJPwQo_EQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQIRJPwQo_EQ&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=fbd4ab0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QIRJPwQo_EQ</a><br />\n<br />\nFull Video : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o34hyIVn2oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do34hyIVn2oU&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=db15ef08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o34hyIVn2oU</a>"},{"pid":"372da4f48d2b178fcf5b662e97d0e286883d3079","tid":2442023,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BoTP30iLRuI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBoTP30iLRu